# plugins/ is a runtime mount point, not a source tree: real plugins live in
# their own repositories and are dropped here at deploy/dev time. Only the
# reference/example plugins that document the SDK contract are tracked.
*
!.gitignore
!.gitkeep
!ExamplePlugin.php
!HelloWorld/
!HelloWorld/**
!UiKitShowcase/
!UiKitShowcase/**
!DemoCatalog/
!DemoCatalog/**
